This project is my personal chess website for personalized study.
I will create the frontend in React and make a simple UI with login
and the ability to link external account. The backend will be in Java,
using Spring Boot, which will communicate with the database. I will 
create a Python ML model to take in the users past games to give a 
training regimen. Finally, I will create my own chess engine in C++ that
the user can mess around with.